♪Kenangan yang membakar terperangkap di tekakku♪

16
00:01:08,300 --> 00:01:11,290
♪Membakar habis kehangatan yang pernah kita kongsi♪

17
00:01:11,290 --> 00:01:13,800
♪Aku akan lenyap
dengan bayangan lilin♪

18
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:15,700
♪Putuskan ikatan dan tinggal sendirian♪

19
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:18,340
♪Lepaskanmu♪

20
00:01:18,550 --> 00:01:21,240
♪Kesedihanmu kekal ketika kau menoleh ke belakang♪

21
00:01:21,240 --> 00:01:23,150
♪Kerinduan ini telah menghabiskan tenagaku♪

22
00:01:23,150 --> 00:01:26,460
♪Kita pernah bersumpah untuk tua bersama♪

23
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:29,050
♪Tetapi jika takdir tidak bersalah, mengapa♪

24
00:01:29,050 --> 00:01:33,460
♪Adakah ia memainkan lagu air mata ini
untukku seorang?♪

25
00:01:34,340 --> 00:01:39,580
=Takdir Cinta=
(Diadaptasi dari novel Lin Nan, Takdir Cinta.)

26
00:01:39,630 --> 00:01:42,400
=Episod 6=

27
00:01:42,766 --> 00:01:45,720
(Kediaman Putera Jin)

28
00:01:48,900 --> 00:01:51,209
(Kediaman Putera Jin)

29
00:01:51,220 --> 00:01:53,020
Abang, Permaisuri Jin,
selamat pagi.

30
00:01:53,022 --> 00:01:53,800
Pagi.

31
00:01:54,550 --> 00:01:55,390
Jadi,

32
00:01:55,550 --> 00:01:56,780
apa yang terjadi pada suaramu?

33
00:01:58,580 --> 00:01:59,110
Tiada apa-apa.

34
00:02:00,550 --> 00:02:01,511
Itu tidak penting.

35
00:02:01,630 --> 00:02:03,700
Yang penting kita semua berseronok hari ini.

36
00:02:05,300 --> 00:02:05,700
Ayuh.

37
00:02:07,110 --> 00:02:08,460
(Dengan suara itu?)

38
00:02:09,020 --> 00:02:10,733
(Mari lihat berapa banyak keseronokan yang kau boleh dapat.)

39
00:02:13,830 --> 00:02:14,800
Berhenti duduk di situ.

40
00:02:15,790 --> 00:02:17,140
Ayuh! Cepatlah.

41
00:02:23,175 --> 00:02:27,060
(Persatuan Segalanya)

42
00:02:27,110 --> 00:02:27,670
Sayang,

43
00:02:28,070 --> 00:02:30,350
Bukankah Ayah kata kita tak boleh keluar hari ini?

44
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:33,350
Ini kali pertama kita keluar.

45
00:02:33,510 --> 00:02:35,950
Saya tak mahu dia tahu.

46
00:02:36,390 --> 00:02:37,270
Ji Mo,

47
00:02:37,550 --> 00:02:38,700
ke mana kamu nak pergi?

48
00:02:38,790 --> 00:02:39,950
Mari, sekarang!

49
00:02:40,790 --> 00:02:41,670
Jangan lari, Ji Mo!

50
00:02:41,670 --> 00:02:42,300
Ke tepi!

51
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:42,990
Ji Mo!

52
00:02:45,300 --> 00:02:47,180
Kamu dah tak hormatkan aku
lepas dapat isteri.

53
00:02:47,580 --> 00:02:48,580
Tak sangka.

54
00:02:51,740 --> 00:02:54,230
Hari itu kamu nampak berminat dengan layang-layang.

55
00:02:54,510 --> 00:02:55,230
Jadi, saya buat satu.

56
00:02:55,860 --> 00:02:56,790
Kamu suka tak?

57
00:02:58,420 --> 00:02:59,900
Kamu memang berbakat, Putera Yunnuo.

58
00:03:00,140 --> 00:03:00,950
Lukisan yang hebat.

59
00:03:01,670 --> 00:03:02,830
Corak awan itu

60
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:04,620
benar-benar menarik perhatian.

61
00:03:05,390 --> 00:03:06,350
Saya gembira kamu suka.

62
00:03:08,350 --> 00:03:09,790
Awan ini...

63
00:03:09,830 --> 00:03:11,555
Biar saya tunjuk cara nak terbangkannya.

64
00:03:14,740 --> 00:03:16,110
Bila bab main layang-layang,

65
00:03:16,110 --> 00:03:17,270
saya pakarnya di sini.

66
00:03:20,420 --> 00:03:21,377
Jiufeng?

67
00:03:31,510 --> 00:03:32,140
Yunnuo.

68
00:03:32,990 --> 00:03:34,510
Kemahiran melukis kamu sudah menurun.

69
00:03:35,070 --> 00:03:36,700
Reka bentuk pada layang-layang itu

70
00:03:36,700 --> 00:03:37,950
nampak sangat tidak kena.

71
00:03:38,350 --> 00:03:40,700
Aliya, awak pun rasa begitu, kan?

72
00:03:42,990 --> 00:03:43,860
Abang, betul kata abang.

73
00:03:44,210 --> 00:03:46,170
Kali ini saya memang agak tergesa-gesa.

74
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,210
Lain kali, saya akan lukis yang lebih cantik.

75
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,170
Saya rasa awan itu nampak cantik.

76
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:55,050
Putera Yunnuo, awan yang awak lukis ini

77
00:03:55,050 --> 00:03:56,610
mesti ada maksud tertentu, kan?

78
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,280
Sebenarnya, awan ini...

79
00:03:59,330 --> 00:04:01,520
Ia cuma awan yang mengejar bulan,

80
00:04:01,610 --> 00:04:04,370
kabus di atas gunung, awan berlapis, dan seumpamanya.

81
00:04:04,610 --> 00:04:05,680
Aliya, kalau awak suka,

82
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,330
saya boleh lukiskan satu untuk awak sendiri.

83
00:04:07,330 --> 00:04:08,210
Macam mana?

84
00:04:09,370 --> 00:04:10,560
Oh, sudahlah.

85
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,000
Awan awak

86
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,000
tak boleh lawan dengan dia punya.

87
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:14,560
Pulangkan semula!

88
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,840
Putera Yunnuo, mari kita main layang-layang.

89
00:04:19,400 --> 00:04:19,920
Baiklah.

90
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:23,650
Tuanku.

91
00:04:23,770 --> 00:04:26,040
Bukankah tuanku cuba jodohkan mereka berdua? Jadi kenapa...

92
00:04:35,210 --> 00:04:37,040
(Mengapa saya benar-benar rasa)

93
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,600
(agak cemburu sekarang?)

94
00:04:58,960 --> 00:04:59,520
Putera Yunnuo.

95
00:05:00,330 --> 00:05:02,040
Layang-layang corak awan yang tuanku buat itu

96
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,280
nampak rawak pada pandangan pertama,

97
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:05,580
tapi nampaknya ada susunan di sebaliknya.

98
00:05:05,700 --> 00:05:06,520
Betul tak?

99
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:10,250
Awak nampak sangat berminat dengan lukisan awan itu.

100
00:05:11,690 --> 00:05:12,770
Cuma ingin tahu saja.

101
00:05:15,130 --> 00:05:16,690
Nah, pegang macam ini.

102
00:05:22,340 --> 00:05:23,230
Tuanku.

103
00:05:23,450 --> 00:05:25,160
Semuanya berjalan seperti yang tuanku rancang.

104
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,780
Tolak saya ke sana.

105
00:05:30,511 --> 00:05:31,450
Tarik sedikit.

106
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,330
Kamu buat semuanya salah.

107
00:05:35,330 --> 00:05:36,210
Buat seperti saya.

108
00:05:41,890 --> 00:05:43,160
Nampak? Kambing di sana.

109
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:44,130
Mari kita pergi tengok mereka.

110
00:05:44,250 --> 00:05:44,690
Baik.

111
00:05:44,770 --> 00:05:45,090
Mari.

112
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:46,720
Jiufeng.

113
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:49,090
Pergi beli semua kambing itu.

114
00:05:49,890 --> 00:05:50,600
Baik, saya akan lakukan.

115
00:05:54,250 --> 00:05:55,580
Pemandangan di sini sangat indah.

116
00:05:55,650 --> 00:05:56,720
Saya rasa segar serta-merta.

117
00:05:57,070 --> 00:05:58,160
Sayang, cerita jenis apa

118
00:05:58,210 --> 00:05:59,940
yang kamu ingin tulis kali ini?

119
00:06:00,280 --> 00:06:03,090
Saya ingin menulis kisah tentang takdir yang tersilap

120
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:04,770
yang membawa kepada cinta.

121
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:08,040
Dua gadis dengan impian berbeza akhirnya

122
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:09,450
mengalami perubahan hidup

123
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:11,210
kerana satu kemalangan.

124
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,250
Salah seorang daripada mereka saya tak pernah jumpa.

125
00:06:13,690 --> 00:06:15,410
Saya mahu wataknya berdasarkan peribadi kamu.

126
00:06:15,670 --> 00:06:16,720
Bagaimana dengan seorang lagi?

127
00:06:17,890 --> 00:06:19,130
Yang seorang lagi...

128
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:24,890
Manman!

129
00:06:26,010 --> 00:06:26,720
Puteri Aliya?

130
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:38,720
Fang.

131
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,570
Mari kita pergi

132
00:06:39,570 --> 00:06:40,400
bermain di sana.

133
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,480
Tapi Manman...

134
00:06:42,690 --> 00:06:43,250
Yuetao.

135
00:06:43,890 --> 00:06:44,770
Bukankah aku dah beritahu kamu?

136
00:06:45,250 --> 00:06:46,977
Saya sudah berkahwin sekarang.
Saya Permaisuri Jin.

137
00:06:51,666 --> 00:06:52,755
Permaisuri Jin,

138
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,690
nampaknya ada seseorang di sana

139
00:06:54,890 --> 00:06:56,040
sedang melambai ke arah kamu.

140
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:58,010
Dia juga memanggil kamu Manman.

141
00:07:00,690 --> 00:07:02,090
Mungkin kamu tersalah dengar.

142
00:07:02,450 --> 00:07:04,360
Mungkin mereka maksudkan "jalan perlahan-lahan".

143
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,810
Matahari hampir terbenam.

144
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,570
Kita dah keluar seharian. Saya pun penat.

145
00:07:13,450 --> 00:07:15,600
Mari cari tempat untuk berehat.

146
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,570
Baiklah.

147
00:07:30,210 --> 00:07:32,770
Sayang, saya tak sangka awak boleh lari secepat itu.

148
00:07:33,890 --> 00:07:34,480
Ya.

149
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:37,090
Awak tahu,

150
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:41,960
senaman membantu membuka meridian.

151
00:07:42,090 --> 00:07:43,600
Ia juga menyegarkan fikiran.

152
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:46,280
Awak yang beritahu saya semua itu.

153
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,210
Saya sangat gembira

154
00:07:48,690 --> 00:07:50,040
kerana awak ingat

155
00:07:50,250 --> 00:07:51,450
semua yang saya katakan.

156
00:07:52,210 --> 00:07:55,010
Oh ya, kita terserempak dengan Manman hari ini.

157
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:56,770
Kenapa dia

158
00:07:56,770 --> 00:07:58,250
bersama sekumpulan orang yang saya tak kenal?

159
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:00,360
Adakah mereka semua kawan dia?

160
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,010
Mungkin.

161
00:08:04,450 --> 00:08:05,600
Awak kenal dia.

162
00:08:06,090 --> 00:08:07,040
Dia memang ramai kawan.

163
00:08:13,450 --> 00:08:16,480
Bintang-bintang sangat indah malam ini.

164
00:08:17,450 --> 00:08:17,920
Ya.

165
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:22,480
Sayang, apa nama

166
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:23,920
bintang-bintang yang paling terang?

167
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,360
Yang itu?

168
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,360
Itu ialah Biduk Besar.

169
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:28,770
Bila kita sesat,

170
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,650
ia membantu menunjukkan jalan.

171
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,290
Dalam hatiku,

172
00:08:33,690 --> 00:08:36,410
kaulah bintang paling terang di langit malam.

173
00:08:40,530 --> 00:08:43,450
Sayang, awak belum habiskan cerita tadi.

174
00:08:43,450 --> 00:08:44,360
Awak biarkan tergantung.

175
00:08:44,810 --> 00:08:45,960
Jadi,

176
00:08:47,090 --> 00:08:48,240
awak suka cerita itu?

177
00:08:49,170 --> 00:08:51,170
Saya suka setiap cerita yang awak ceritakan.

178
00:08:52,090 --> 00:08:54,120
Mulai sekarang, bila awak tulis cerita baru,

179
00:08:54,570 --> 00:08:56,330
awak mesti bacakan kepada saya dulu.

180
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,210
Lihat betul-betul.

181
00:09:07,170 --> 00:09:07,960
Jangan berkelip.

182
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:09,530
Kenapa?

183
00:09:09,955 --> 00:09:11,511
Sebab pada saat seperti ini,

184
00:09:12,570 --> 00:09:14,120
dalam cerita cinta saya,

185
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,840
ada bintang jatuh melintasi langit.

186
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,120
Betul ke?

187
00:09:22,170 --> 00:09:23,530
Sayang, tengok!

188
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:24,810
Bintang jatuh!

189
00:09:25,170 --> 00:09:26,120
Hebatnya!

190
00:09:26,330 --> 00:09:27,600
Ya, sangat ajaib!

191
00:09:30,930 --> 00:09:31,530
Sayang!

192
00:09:31,690 --> 00:09:32,600
Ada satu lagi!

193
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:34,880
Awak rasa akan ada yang ketiga?

194
00:09:37,090 --> 00:09:37,570
Sayang,

195
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,170
awak boleh pegang tangan saya sekarang.

196
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:48,960
Sayang?

197
00:09:50,210 --> 00:09:50,930
Sayang?

198
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:52,480
Sayang!

199
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,290
Bangun, sayang!

200
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:57,760
Lihat! Ada bintang jatuh!

201
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,170
Kalau kamu buat hajat sekarang,

202
00:10:01,210 --> 00:10:02,410
hajat kamu akan jadi kenyataan.

203
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,050
Betul ke?

204
00:10:03,930 --> 00:10:05,410
Cepat! Buat hajat!

205
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:09,760
Kamu tahu tak?

206
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,360
Ini kali pertama saya

207
00:10:11,410 --> 00:10:13,090
melihat sesuatu seperti ini dalam hidup saya.

208
00:10:16,050 --> 00:10:16,960
Masa saya kecil dulu,

209
00:10:17,690 --> 00:10:19,000
saya pernah baca buku astronomi

210
00:10:20,210 --> 00:10:22,720
tentang komet yang bersinar seperti siang
dan bintang jatuh seperti hujan.

211
00:10:23,410 --> 00:10:24,210
Dan bila saya lihat sekarang,

212
00:10:24,450 --> 00:10:25,290
ia sangat menakjubkan.

213
00:10:25,290 --> 00:10:27,570
Tapi komet sebenarnya dianggap petanda buruk.

214
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:30,930
Biasanya ia meramalkan kekacauan dan peperangan di seluruh negeri.

215
00:10:34,210 --> 00:10:36,170
Tak bolehkah kamu fikir secara lebih positif?

216
00:10:37,170 --> 00:10:38,760
Saya cuma nyatakan fakta.

217
00:10:39,290 --> 00:10:40,690
Tanya Yunnuo kalau kamu tak percaya.

218
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:42,120
Pernahkah dia baca apa-apa yang mengatakan

219
00:10:42,290 --> 00:10:43,570
komet itu petanda baik?

220
00:10:48,450 --> 00:10:49,210
Memang betul.

221
00:10:50,210 --> 00:10:53,360
Komet juga dikenali sebagai pembawa nasib malang.

222
00:10:58,360 --> 00:11:01,050
Sama ada bintang itu petanda baik atau buruk hanyalah kepercayaan manusia.

223
00:11:01,640 --> 00:11:03,760
Ada yang kata bintang bertuah bermaksud perjalanan yang lancar di hadapan.

224
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:06,840
Ada yang kata bintang malapetaka membawa nasib malang.

225
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:08,360
Tapi bintang hanyalah bintang.

226
00:11:08,570 --> 00:11:10,570
Bagaimana kita boleh salahkan bintang atas nasib kita?

227
00:11:19,930 --> 00:11:21,810
Bintang kecil, ini bukan salah kamu.

228
00:11:22,530 --> 00:11:24,240
Jangan pedulikan kata-kata orang yang tidak tahu apa-apa.

229
00:11:24,880 --> 00:11:26,050
Kamu perlu menjadi kuat.

230
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,410
Bersinarlah dengan terang.

231
00:11:27,930 --> 00:11:29,170
Dengan cara itu,

232
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:31,210
kamu akan menerangi seluruh langit malam.

233
00:11:34,690 --> 00:11:35,530
Ibu saya pernah beritahu saya

234
00:11:35,530 --> 00:11:37,410
bahawa saya juga adalah bintang kecil.

235
00:11:37,622 --> 00:11:40,422
Bintang kecil pun boleh bersinar terang.

236
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:43,360
Dan kamu adalah awan kecil.

237
00:11:45,050 --> 00:11:47,240
Bila kamu sudah menjadi awan besar,

238
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,240
kamu tidak akan takut pada apa-apa pun.

239
00:11:57,450 --> 00:11:59,270
Putera Yunnuo, apa yang sedang kamu fikirkan?

240
00:12:00,410 --> 00:12:00,960
Saya...

241
00:12:03,760 --> 00:12:05,210
